children.name: p
children.text: Online courses can be so much more than just video and text. With Moodle, you can create engaging lectures that your learners will love.

children.name: div
children.text: Moodle has been the world's most popular open-source learning management system since 2005 because it is easy to use, affordable and adaptable to any educational environment. Today, Moodle has grown into one of the most popular LMSs in the world with over 18 million users and 15 thousand schools using it every day.

children.name: h1
children.text: How to make interactive Moodle courses?

children.name: p
children.text: Many educators are looking for new ways to engage their students and make learning more interactive. But creating fun courses shouldn't be that difficult. That's why we chose to add H5P plug-in to all of our Moodle installations. We believe that H5P can be a valuable tool in your course development. This open-source project contains a diverse group of tools that allow you to create interactive courses with no programming skills required, giving teachers or instructional designers the ability to integrate multimedia content into their lessons easily and without additional costs.
